title: Cubs win NL Division Series, beat Cardinals 6-4 in Game 4
text:
> Top News Cubs win NL Division Series, beat Cardinals 6-4 in Game 4 Chicago Cubs relief pitcher Pedro Strop reacts as the Cubs first baseman Anthony Rizzo (44) tags out St. Louis Cardinals' Kolten Wong (16) during the eighth inning of Game 4 in baseball's National League Division Series, Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015, in Chicago.
